{ White should exchange the light-squared bishops now to weaken the defence of the d5-pawn. }
16... Bxa6 17. Rxa6 cxd4 18. exd4 e6 19. Ra7
{ White's pieces are very active. White can play on the queenside with Qe2, Rea1. Black must be very careful with the tactical threats. }
