8. Qa4+ { White tries to activate the queen and keep the bishop on d6. } 8...
Nc6 9. Qa3 cxd2+ 10. Nxd2 Bd7 11. Bd3 Ng8
{ This move is very hard to find over the board. Black must find this knight maneuver in order to be able to castle, otherwise, he has a difficult position.  11...Qa5  12.Qb3  Qb6  13.Rc1  Qxb3  14.Nxb3  . Even without the queens, the bishop on d6 is still quite annoying for Black. }
12. Rc1 Nge7
