{ White has enough compensation, but no more than that. This is a waiting game where we need to be patient. If Black takes on e4 too early, White can recapture with Ne4 and bring the knight to d6  (after the bishop retreats to g3 or h2)  . Our plan is to improve the position to a maximum with h3, Bg3, Nf3. At some point, the position will be open and the bishop pair will become quite powerful. }
