{ 5.Nb5  is my recommendation inPart I.  White should play it before Black castles, so Black does not have the extra option of 6...Ne8  to defend the c7-pawn. }
5... O-O 6. Nb5 Na6 7. h3 c6 8. Nc3 Nc7 9. Bd3 b6 10. O-O Bb7 11. e4
